The usual thing:

./configure
make
make install

CONFIGURE OPTIONS

--with-fltk-dir=...     Specify where Fltk resides.
--with-fltk2            Use Fltk 2 (cvs) and not Fltk 1.0.7.
                        This is required to get Flek to compile with FLTK_2.
--with-no-gl            Don't compile OpenGL support.
